 well here it goes went to Nam in nov 1967 just turned 18 in   August that year. I now was a Green Mean Fighting Machine in the  U.S.M.C..  Uncle Sam's Misguided Children.<br>
  Flew as a gunner in a UH1E Huey Gunship.<br>
Seen alot of country from above . It was a pritty place out in the Valley's..<br>
  Took me till 9yrs ago to quite drinking and fighting in bars but my head is on right again thank's to a loving family..<br>
  But if my country ever asked of me to do it again  I would pack up and be ready in 5 min..<br>
  I thought  I was there for agood reason and I would  help anybody try to be free..<br>
Freedom has a meaning those have fought for it the protected will never Know.<br>
 Please rember are POW's and MIA's they went for you so bring them all home. Dead or Alive. <br>
  We owe them that. DON'T WE.
